snippet.title: Venus Looks for Jupiter - Opening Moments
snippet.description:
RELEASES MAY 5 - https://dancingengie.itch.io/venus

A short first-person parkour game about searching for love high and low AND ALSO shooting red objects with a big, fat revolver. Mirror's Edge crossed with Titanfall 2 with the artstyle of Killer7.

Based on, named after and featuring Israeli rock song "Noga Mechapeset Tzedek" by Elisha Banai & The Forty Thieves: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BIrbfOKfxbs

Follow me on Twitter at https://twitter.com/DancingEngie
Or check out my other work at https://dancingengie.xyz
